          "author": {
            "login": "ConcaveTrillion"
          },
          "body": "Context: Discovered while working on pd-ocr-labeler-spa#267. The glyph epic (#267-#270) is blocked because `pd_book_tools.ocr.glyph_annotations` (post-#163: uppercased `LigatureKind`, `LONG_ST` rename, `OE`/`AE` added, Option K vocab) is merged to `main` but the latest tag `v0.12.0` is ~27 commits behind and lacks the module entirely.\n\nDownstream repos cannot pin a release containing it; SHA pins violate workspace policy.\n\nAction: cut `v0.13.0` from `main` so pd-ocr-labeler-spa can run `make upgrade-pd-book-tools` against a tag.",
